{"id": "ivos062", "name": "Cam_St10_702_12_29", "res": null, "contents": [[{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["MUTE"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Robot_Move_01", "Raises Gun"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kouhei"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">NEKO! Be careful!</font>\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">WAAAHHH!</font>\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["GunShot_03", "Gunshots"], "content": ""}, {"id": 5, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Glass_Break", "Torso Blasted"], "content": ""}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "......!?\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon_Helmet", "Head Dismantled"], "content": ""}, {"id": 8, "type": "image", "attrs": ["ivos6201"], "content": ""}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">Xenon!?</font>\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Alright? Give me your hand.\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "<i>... *sob*... *sob*</i>!\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "Aigh-ya, look who just arrived.\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "... What happened?\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "Precisely what we were worried would happen. Our enemy has already begun making moves. As you can see, it's a disaster of epic proportions.\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "In any case, this bunch is dealt with. Let's go somewhere with more space, it's too dangerous here.\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→Signal Switches]</i>\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Running_Step", "Sprints"], "content": ""}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Here!\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_2", "Footsteps"], "content": ""}, {"id": 20, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Trigger", "Raises Gun"], "content": ""}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "Waaah! Don't shoot! I'm with you!\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "JOE...?\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "Hayato!?\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "What are you doing here? What are you doing with all these people here?\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "Saving the peeps! The Administration Bureau doesn't have enough to deal with such a disaster.\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "... These people, are they gang members? Is that alright?\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "You haven't heard? Anytime something this big happens, good and bad work together. The gangs aren't all like Baro, those bastards.\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Alright, we'll leave you to it. There are a lot more people trapped in there.\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "You're not staying to help?\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "I've got to bring NEKO and her family to the ambulance, then I've got to leave right away. We know how to stop all of this.\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "Got it. Hey! Everybody! Come with me.\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "JOE, wait. You all got guns?\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "Eh? Oh yeah... I heard they're something like Architects? They still in there?\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Even though the road in is basically all cleared out, I really don't know how many there are and I don't know where they're coming from. Listen, their core is in the back of the skull area. Attacking anywhere else doesn't do anything. Also, take this device. If you can't take care of them in time, just press this. It'll paralyze them temporarily, for about 10 seconds.\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "Alright, I'll take care of 'em... Hey, glad to see you back on your feet.\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Hey... you guys be careful.\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_2", "Footsteps"], "content": ""}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "Mr. Jackson.\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......? The gossip reporter... whatta you want?\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "Hayato told me everything. I just wanted to say that because of my work, I owe you an apology. Now I know what kind of person you really are.\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......\nIf you want to report the truth, I'd advise you and Hayato to not go in there. You can't take these things on. I recorded these images for intel. I'll send 'em to you. Use it wisely.\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "......!\nUnderstood. Thank you.\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→Signal Switches]</i>\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "NEKO... you okay?\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "Yea... thanks for coming and saving everybody. I'm so happy you pulled yourself together.\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "I'm sorry... for what happened in Node 03. The stuff I said...\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "No worries! You just said all that 'cuz you wanted to protect NEKO and get me away. I didn't hold it against you.\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "... We're here. Come on, get in the ambulance. Can't reveal our identities.\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "... NEKO... NEKO's not badly injured. NEKO wants to go with you!\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kouhei"], "content": "No way! What are you saying!? Can't you see how dangerous the stuff they're facing is!?\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Listen to your father. There's nothing you can do to help.\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "Oh......\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "Mr. Jackson, we must be going.\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Okay. Get going, and be careful.\n"}, {"id": 55, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[Signal Lost]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["MUTE"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Robot_Move_01", "殴る"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kouhei"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">NEKO！危ない！</font>\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">わああああ！！</font>\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["GunShot_03", "銃声"], "content": ""}, {"id": 5, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Glass_Break", "機械が壊れる"], "content": ""}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "……！？\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon_Helmet", "ヘルメットを取る"], "content": ""}, {"id": 8, "type": "image", "attrs": ["ivos6201"], "content": ""}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">Xenon！？</font>\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "無事か？ほら、手。\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "っ……うう～！\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "おやおや。ヒーローの登場かな？\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……一体何があったんです。\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "最も恐れていたことが起きてしまったのだよ。\n敵は行動を開始した。\nまあ、見た通りだとも。\nひどいありさまだ。\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "とにかく、ひとまずは大丈夫だ。\n移動しよう。ここは危険すぎる。\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→シグナル切り替え]</i>\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Running_Step", "走る"], "content": ""}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "こっちだ！\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_2", "足音"], "content": ""}, {"id": 20, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Trigger", "銃を構える"], "content": ""}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "うおおおい！撃つな！撃たないで！俺敵じゃない！\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "JOE……？\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "隼人！？\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "なんでお前たちが一緒にいるんだ？\nそんなに大勢連れてこんなところで何をしている？\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "救助に決まってんだろ！\nこんな大規模な崩壊なんだ。\n管理局だけじゃ人手が足りないだろって。\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……この人たちは……裏社会の人間だろ？\n大丈夫なのか？\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "知らねーの？\nこういう時はいつも表とか裏とか関係なく助け合ってんだよ。\nヤクザが全部バローみたいなクソ野郎ばっかだと思うなよ？\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "なら、ここは頼んだ。\nまだ閉じ込められてる人が大勢いる。\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "お前たちは残らないのか？\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "俺はまずNEKOとNEKOの家族を救急車まで送る。\nそれから……すべてを終わらせに行く。\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "オッケー。\nおーい！みんな！こっち！\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "JOE、待て。\nお前たちなら、拳銃持ってるよな？\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "え？あるっちゃあるけど……\n敵はアーキテクトみたいな奴らなんだろ？\nまだ中にいるのか？\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "ここに来るまでにかなりの数を潰してきた。\nだが、相手の数がわからない。\nいつどこに現れるかも……\nいいか？よく聞け。\nあいつらの急所は後頭部だ。他の場所を攻撃しても効かない。\nそれからこれを。\nどうしても応戦が間に合わないって時はこれを押せ。\n一時的に敵の動きを止めることができる。\nとはいっても約10秒程度だが。\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "任せろって……なぁ、俺嬉しいよ。\nお前がまた立ち上がってくれてさ。\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "あぁ……気を付けろよ。\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_2", "足音"], "content": ""}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "Jacksonさん。\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……？\nゴシップ記者か……まだ何か？\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "全部、隼人から聞きました。\n私は、ただあなたに謝罪がしたくて……\n今なら分かります。あなたがどんな人なのか。\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "………\nもし真相を報道したければ、中には入らないことだ。\nあいつらはあんたたちの手に負えるものじゃない。\nデータ収集のために撮った映像だが……今送った。正しく使ってくれ。\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "……！\nはい！ありがとうございます！\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→シグナル切り替え]</i>\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "NEKO……大丈夫か？\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "うん。助けてくれてありがとうね。\n立ち直れたみたいでよかった。\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Node03では……悪かった。\nあんな風に……\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "いいって！\nだってXenonはNEKOを守るためにわざとあんな風に言ったんでしょ？\nNEKO気にしてないよ。\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……着いた。早く乗れ。\nあまり顔を見られるわけにはいかない。\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "……NEKOは……NEKOはそんなにひどいケガしてない！\nだから……っ！一緒に連れて行って！\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kouhei"], "content": "ダメだ！何を言ってるんだ！？\nさっきのを見ていてもわからないのか！危険なんだぞ！？\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "お父さんの言うことを聞くんだ。\nお前が来ても何もできることはない。\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "……っ……\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "Mr. Jackson、そろそろ行くとしよう。\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "はい。\nNEKO、気を付けるんだぞ。\n"}, {"id": 55, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[電波切断]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["MUTE"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Robot_Move_01", "舉拳"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kouhei"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">NEKO！小心！</font>\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">哇啊啊啊！</font>\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["GunShot_03", "槍聲"], "content": ""}, {"id": 5, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Glass_Break", "機體損毀"], "content": ""}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "……！？\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon_Helmet", "卸除頭盔"], "content": ""}, {"id": 8, "type": "image", "attrs": ["ivos6201"], "content": ""}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">Xenon！？</font>\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "沒事吧？手給我。\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "嗚……嗚嗚！\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "哎呀，看看是誰登場了。\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……這裡發生什麼事了？\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "發生了我們最擔心的事呢，對方已經開始行動了，如你所見，這大規模的災害。\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "總之暫時解決這一批了，先到空曠的地方吧，這裡太危險了。\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→切換訊號]</i>\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Running_Step", "奔跑"], "content": ""}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "這邊！\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_2", "腳步"], "content": ""}, {"id": 20, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Trigger", "舉槍"], "content": ""}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "哇哇哇！別開槍！自己人！\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "JOE……？\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "Hayato！？\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "為什麼你們會在一起？你們帶那麼大群人在這裡做什麼？\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "來救難啊！這麼大的坍塌只靠管理局的人根本不夠。\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……這些人，是黑社會的人吧？沒問題嗎？\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "你不知道嗎？每當出這種事黑白兩道都會合作的，黑社會不是全都像 Baro 那些混蛋。\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "那就拜託你們了，還有很多人被困在裡面。\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "你們不留下來幫忙嗎？\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "我得先把 NEKO 一家人送上救護車，然後就得走了，我們知道怎麼阻止這場災難。\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "我知道了。喂！大家！跟我來。\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "JOE，等等。你們都有帶槍吧？\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "咦？有是有……我聽說了，是類似建造者的東西對吧？它們還在裡面嗎？\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "雖然出來的路上已經清得差不多了，但我真的不知道數量有多少，也不知道它們從哪裡冒出來的。聽好，他們的核心在後腦杓的位置，打其他地方都沒用。還有這個裝置拿著，處理不來就按這個鈕，可以暫時癱瘓它們的行動，大概十秒。\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "交給我吧……喂，很高興看到你振作起來。\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "嗯……你們小心點。\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_2", "腳步"], "content": ""}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "Jackson 先生。\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……？報八卦的記者……還有什麼事嗎？\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "我全都從 Hayato 那聽說了，我只是想說之前因為工作的關係，對你感到很抱歉。我現在理解你是個什麼樣的人了。\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n如果是想報真相，我勸妳跟 Hayato 別進去比較好，那些東西不是你們可以應付的。我為了蒐集資料錄了這些影像，傳給妳了，好好運用吧。\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "……！\n我知道了，謝謝。\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→切換訊號]</i>\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "NEKO……妳沒事吧？\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "嗯，謝謝你回來救大家。你能振作起來真的太好了。\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "在 Node 03 的時候……很抱歉，對妳說了那些話……\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "沒關係啦！你是為了保護 NEKO 才故意用那些話把 NEKO 趕走的，NEKO 沒有放在心上。\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……到了，快上救護車吧，我們的身份不方便露面。\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "……NEKO……NEKO 的傷沒有很嚴重，NEKO 想跟你們一起去！\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kouhei"], "content": "不行！妳在說什麼傻話！？沒有看到他們面對的是多危險的事嗎！？\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "聽妳爸的話，妳來也幫不上忙的。\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "唔……\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "Mr. Jackson，我們走吧。\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "好。你們快走吧，小心點。\n"}, {"id": 55, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["MUTE"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Robot_Move_01", "주먹을 든다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kouhei"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">NEKO! 小조심해!</font>\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">우아아아아!</font>\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["GunShot_03", "총성"], "content": ""}, {"id": 5, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Glass_Break", "기체가 파손된다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "......! ? \n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon_Helmet", "헬멧을 벗는다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 8, "type": "image", "attrs": ["ivos6201"], "content": ""}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">Xenon! ? </font>\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "무사했나? 자, 손.\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "흑......흐흑! \n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "오호라~ 이게 누구신지.\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......여기서 대체 무슨 일이 일어난 거지?\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "우리가 가장 우려했던 일이 일어나고 말았지요. 적은 이미 행동을 개시했습니다. 보시는 것처럼, 이런 대규모의 재난이 일어나고 말았죠.\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "일단 이곳은 해결된 것 같군. 우선 이동하자. 여긴 너무 위험해.\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→신호 변경]</i>\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Running_Step", "달려간다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "여기다!\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_2", "발걸음"], "content": ""}, {"id": 20, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Trigger", "총을 꺼낸다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "우아아앗! 쏘지 마! 쏘지 마! 같은 편이라고!\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "JOE......? \n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "Hayato! ? \n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "어째서 너희들이 함께...? 그렇게 많은 사람들을 데리고 뭘 하려고 했던 거야?\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "당연히 구조 작업을 벌이고 있었지! 이 정도 규모의 사건은 관리국 사람만으로는 부족하니까.\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......이 자들, 모두 조직 사람들이잖아? 정말 괜찮은 거야?\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "아직도 모르겠어? 지금 같은 때는 너도 나도 다 함께 힘을 합쳐야될 때라고! 조직에 있는 사람이라고 모두 Baro같은 녀석들만 있는 게 아니라니까!\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "그럼 여긴 너희들에게 맡길게. 아직 많은 사람들이 안에 갇혀있어.\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "너희들은 어쩌고? \n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "난 NEKO 일가족을 구급차로 보내자마자 바로 떠나야만 해. 이 모든 재앙들을 막기 위해서.\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "알겠어. 이봐, 모두들! 날 따라와!\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "JOE, 잠깐. 너희들 모두 총은 가지고 있겠지?\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "응? 있긴 있는데... 적은 아키텍트에 가까운 녀석들인가? 아직 안에 있는 거야?\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "오면서 꽤 많이 제거하긴 했지만, 그래도 아직 정확한 숫자는 파악하지 못했어. 언제 어디서 나타날지도 몰라... 그러니 잘 들어.\n녀석들의 코어는 바로 뒤통수에 위치해있어. 그곳이 바로 약점이다. 다른 곳은 공격해도 소용없어. 이 디바이스를 줄 테니 처리하기 어려워지면 이 버튼을 누르도록 해. 잠시나마 녀석들의 움직임을 느리게 만들 수 있어. 그래도 10초뿐이니까 그 안에 해결해야만 해.\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "내게 맡겨... 하하, 이렇게 다시 일어선 모습을 보니 괜히 반갑구먼!\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "그래......조심해라!\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_2", "발걸음"], "content": ""}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "Jackson 씨.\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......? 잡지 기자인가......또 무슨 볼일이지?\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "전부 Hayato에게서 들었어요. \n그저 예전 일에 대한 사과를 하고 싶었습니다.\n이젠 당신이 어떤 사람인지 확실하게 알았어요.\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......\n만약 진실을 보도하고 싶다면 Hayato와 당신은 안으로 들어가지 말라고 충고해주고 싶군. 저것들은 당신들이 감당할 수 있는 상대가 아니야. 이것들은 내가 데이터를 모으기 위해 수집했던 영상 파일들이다. 당신에게 줄 테니, 잘 사용해보라고.\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "......! \n알겠습니다. 고마워요!\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→신호 변경]</i>\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "NEKO......괜찮냐?\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "응. 도와줘서 고마워, 모두들. \n다시 일어서서 다행이야, Xenon.\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Node 03에서의 일은... 사과하마. \n네게 했던 말들은...\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "괜찮다구! 전부 NEKO를 위험으로부터 지키기 위해서, NEKO를 쫓아내려고 일부러 그런 말을 했던 거잖아! \nNEKO는 벌써 다 잊었다구!\n\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......도착했군. 빨리 구급차에 타. 우리들은 아직 신분이 노출되면 곤란한 상황이라.\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "......NEKO......NEKO는 별로 안 다쳤어! NEKO도너희들이랑 같이 가고 싶어!\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kouhei"], "content": "안 돼! 무슨 헛소리를 하는 거니!? 그들이 얼마나 위험한 녀석들과 맞붙고 있었는지 봐놓고도 벌써 잊은 거니!?\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "아버지 말 들어. 네가 도울 수 있는 일은 없어.\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "으윽......\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "Mr. Jackson, 이제 가도록 하죠.\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "알았다.\nNEKO, 빨리 가봐. 조심하고.\n"}, {"id": 55, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[신호 중단]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["MUTE"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Robot_Move_01", "舉拳"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kouhei"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">NEKO！小心！</font>\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">哇啊啊啊！</font>\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["GunShot_03", "槍聲"], "content": ""}, {"id": 5, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Glass_Break", "機體損毀"], "content": ""}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "……！？\n"}, {"id": 7, "type"