s": ["Xenon"], "content": "我得先把 NEKO 一家人送上救護車，然後就得走了，我們知道怎麼阻止這場災難。\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "我知道了。喂！大家！跟我來。\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "JOE，等等。你們都有帶槍吧？\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "咦？有是有……我聽說了，是類似建造者的東西對吧？它們還在裡面嗎？\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "雖然出來的路上已經清得差不多了，但我真的不知道數量有多少，也不知道它們從哪裡冒出來的。聽好，他們的核心在後腦杓的位置，打其他地方都沒用。還有這個裝置拿著，處理不來就按這個鈕，可以暫時癱瘓它們的行動，大概十秒。\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "交給我吧……喂，很高興看到你振作起來。\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "嗯……你們小心點。\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_2", "腳步"], "content": ""}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "Jackson 先生。\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……？報八卦的記者……還有什麼事嗎？\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "我全都從 Hayato 那聽說了，我只是想說之前因為工作的關係，對你感到很抱歉。我現在理解你是個什麼樣的人了。\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n如果是想報真相，我勸妳跟 Hayato 別進去比較好，那些東西不是你們可以應付的。我為了蒐集資料錄了這些影像，傳給妳了，好好運用吧。\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "……！\n我知道了，謝謝。\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→切換訊號]</i>\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "NEKO……妳沒事吧？\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "嗯，謝謝你回來救大家。你能振作起來真的太好了。\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "在 Node 03 的時候……很抱歉，對妳說了那些話……\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "沒關係啦！你是為了保護 NEKO 才故意用那些話把 NEKO 趕走的，NEKO 沒有放在心上。\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……到了，快上救護車吧，我們的身份不方便露面。\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "……NEKO……NEKO 的傷沒有很嚴重，NEKO 想跟你們一起去！\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kouhei"], "content": "不行！妳在說什麼傻話！？沒有看到他們面對的是多危險的事嗎！？\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "聽妳爸的話，妳來也幫不上忙的。\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "唔……\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "Mr. Jackson，我們走吧。\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "好。你們快走吧，小心點。\n"}, {"id": 55, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["MUTE"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Robot_Move_01", "举拳"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kouhei"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">NEKO！小心！ </font>\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">哇啊啊啊！ </font>\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["GunShot_03", "枪声"], "content": ""}, {"id": 5, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Glass_Break", "机体损毁"], "content": ""}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "……！ ？\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon_Helmet", "卸除头盔"], "content": ""}, {"id": 8, "type": "image", "attrs": ["ivos6201"], "content": ""}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">Xenon！ ？ </font>\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "没事吧？手给我。\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "呜……呜呜！\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "哎呀，看看是谁登场了。\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……这里发生什么事了？\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "发生了我们最担心的事呢，对方已经开始行动了，如你所见，这大规模的灾害。\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "总之暂时解决这一批了，先到空旷的地方吧，这里太危险了。\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→切换讯号]</i>\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Running_Step", "奔跑"], "content": ""}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "这边！\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_2", "脚步"], "content": ""}, {"id": 20, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Trigger", "举枪"], "content": ""}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "哇哇哇！别开枪！自己人！\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "JOE……？\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "Hayato！ ？\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "为什么你们会在一起？你们带那么大群人在这里做什么？\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "来救难啊！这么大的坍塌只靠管理局的人根本不够。\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……这些人，是黑社会的人吧？没问题吗？\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "你不知道吗？每当出这种事黑白两道都会合作的，黑社会不是全都像 Baro 那些混蛋。\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "那就拜托你们了，还有很多人被困在里面。\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "你们不留下来帮忙吗？\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "我得先把 NEKO 一家人送上救护车，然后就得走了，我们知道怎么阻止这场灾难。\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "我知道了。喂！大家！跟我来。\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "JOE，等等。你们都有带枪吧？\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "咦？有是有……我听说了，是类似建造者的东西对吧？它们还在里面吗？\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "虽然出来的路上已经清得差不多了，但我真的不知道数量有多少，也不知道它们从哪里冒出来的。听好，他们的核心在后脑杓的位置，打其他地方都没用。还有这个装置拿着，处理不来就按这个钮，可以暂时瘫痪它们的行动，大概十秒。\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "交给我吧……喂，很高兴看到你振作起来。\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "嗯……你们小心点。\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_2", "脚步"], "content": ""}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "Jackson 先生。\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……？报八卦的记者……还有什么事吗？\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "我全都从 Hayato 那听说了，我只是想说之前因为工作的关系，对你感到很抱歉。我现在理解你是个什么样的人了。\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n如果是想报真相，我劝妳跟 Hayato 别进去比较好，那些东西不是你们可以应付的。我为了搜集资料录了这些影像，传给妳了，好好运用吧。\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "……！\n我知道了，谢谢。\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→切换讯号]</i>\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "NEKO……妳没事吧？\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "嗯，谢谢你回来救大家。你能振作起来真的太好了。\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "在 Node 03 的时候……很抱歉，对妳說了那些话……\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "没关系啦！你是为了保护 NEKO 才故意用那些话把 NEKO 赶走的，NEKO 没有放在心上。\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……到了，快上救护车吧，我们的身份不方便露面。\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "……NEKO……NEKO 的伤没有很严重，NEKO 想跟你们一起去！\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kouhei"], "content": "不行！妳在说什么傻话！ ？没有看到他们面对的是多危险的事吗！ ？\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "听妳爸的话，妳来也帮不上忙的。\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "唔……\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "Mr. Jackson，我们走吧。\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "好。你们快走吧，小心点。\n"}, {"id": 55, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[讯号中断]</i>\n"}]]}